{
  "stem": "2833.3",
  "chunk_idx": 13,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 12.8,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "And I was invited and met the American-- new American ambassador to Czechoslovakia, who couldn't go to Prague yet because they were fixing up some building for them to live, and his family wasn't there yet.",
      "word_count": 36
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "And so on that evening at the party, we were talking, and he asked me-- he heard about that I was in camp.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "And he asked me what I'm going to do.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "And I said, you know, I want to get out, because I have family in America, I know that, my father's brother and his wife.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "And I have another aunt and uncle in Canada.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "And they won't let me out now, because it was already very much-- it wasn't-- the communists hadn't taken over.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "But in Prague, they had already their hands in everything.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "And if you had money or if you had, you know, something valuable in real estate or so, they wouldn't let you out till you gave it to them.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "And they couldn't take it away yet legally because they were not really legally, you know, allowed to do that.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So I said, I have to get out illegally.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I, I did it once.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I stayed too long.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I'm not going to do it again.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "He said, I'll fix it for you.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And so he talked to the general that evening.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And he called me and said, I have a friend in Ravensburg, Germany.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I'm going to talk to him, and I think I can help you to get you out.",
      "word_count": 17
    }
  ],
